 | publisher   = Brotherhood of the Bomb: The Tangled Lives and Loyalties of Robert Oppenheimer, Ernest Lawrence, and Edward Teller
 | accessdate  = 2011-03-28
 | lang        = en
}}</ref> и Гордоном Гриффитсом (''Gordon Griffiths'') «закрытым» (секретным) подразделением Коммунистической партии США на факультете Беркли.<ref>{{cite web
 | url         = http://www.brotherhoodofthebomb.com/bhbsource/new_evidence_3.html
 | title       = Excerpts from Gordon Griffith's unpublished memoir
 | author      = 
 | date        = 
